            <div class="title">GIGWA - High-Throughput Genotyping Data Management System</div>
            <div class="desc"><ul>
	<li>Deployed and interoperable with the BMS through <a href="https://brapi.org/" target="_blank">BrAPI</a> (Breeding API), a programming standard developed and used by the global breeding community.</li>
	<li>Developed by <a href="https://www.cirad.fr/en" target="_blank">CIRAD</a>, France&rsquo;s agricultural research and international cooperation organization for the sustainable development of tropical and Mediterranean regions.</li>
</ul>
</div>
            <a href="https://bmspro.io/1740/features?f=4" class="btn btn-solid">Learn more</a>
