          <div class="col-md-5">
            <div class="title">Field data capture</div>
            <div class="desc"><p>Phenotypic data captured in the field easily&nbsp;transfers&nbsp;to and from BMS Pro. Optimized for interoperability with the <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.fieldbook.tracker" target="_blank">KSU FieldBook</a>, an Android application part of the <a href="http://phenoapps.org/apps/" target="_blank">PhenoApps collection</a>.</p>
</div>
            <a href="https://bmspro.io/1740/features?f=17" class="btn btn-solid">Learn more</a>
